# Góc Sách → Movie Review Portal: Architecture & Design Analysis

> Complete architectural, UI/UX, and feature analysis of the **gocsach-laravel** book review project, with adaptation guidance for a **movie review portal** (Letterboxd / Rotten Tomatoes / TMDB style).

---

## 1. Project Structure Analysis

### 1.1 Laravel Folder Architecture

```
gocsach-laravel/
├── app/
│   ├── Http/
│   │   ├── Controllers/         # 18 public controllers
│   │   │   ├── Admin/           # 17 admin controllers (separate namespace)
│   │   │   ├── HomeController   # Homepage data + likes/comments/notifications
│   │   │   ├── BookController   # Listing, detail, search, reviews
│   │   │   ├── PostController   # Review CRUD with moderation workflow
│   │   │   ├── ProfileController# User profiles, avatar frames, badges
│   │   │   ├── AuthController   # Auth with OTP email verification
│   │   │   ├── AuthorController # Author listing & detail
│   │   │   ├── FollowController # Social follow system
│   │   │   ├── CommentController# Comment CRUD
│   │   │   ├── ChatbotController# AI chatbot integration
│   │   │   ├── RankingController# Leaderboard/ranking
│   │   │   └── ReportController # Content moderation/reporting
│   │   └── Middleware/
│   │       ├── CheckAdmin.php       # Admin role guard
│   │       ├── EnsureEmailIsVerified # Email verification
│   │       └── TrackVisitors.php    # Analytics visitor tracking
│   ├── Models/                  # 27 Eloquent models
│   ├── Notifications/           # 14 notification classes
│   └── Observers/               # Model observers
├── resources/views/
│   ├── layouts/
│   │   ├── app.blade.php        # Public layout (Tailwind CDN)
│   │   └── admin.blade.php      # Admin layout
│   ├── partials/                # 8 reusable partials
│   │   ├── header.blade.php     # Mega navigation bar
│   │   ├── footer.blade.php     # Rich footer
│   │   ├── chatbox.blade.php    # AI chatbot widget
│   │   ├── report-modal.blade.php # Report modal (global)
│   │   ├── seasonal-decoration  # Seasonal themes (Christmas, Tet, etc.)
│   │   ├── home_comments.blade.php # AJAX-loaded comments
│   │   ├── user-avatar-with-frame # Avatar + frame component
│   │   └── user-badges.blade.php  # User badge display
│   ├── admin/                   # 16 admin sub-modules
│   └── pages/                   # Static pages (about, contact, etc.)
└── routes/
    └── web.php                  # 376 lines, 4 route groups
```

### 1.2 Controller Organization Pattern

| Pattern | Implementation | Movie Adaptation |
|---------|---------------|-----------------|
| **Entity-Based Controllers** | [BookController](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/BookController.php#11-304), [PostController](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/PostController.php#19-406), [AuthorController](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/AuthorController.php#12-367) | `MovieController`, `ReviewController`, `ActorController` |
| **Admin Namespace Separation** | `App\Http\Controllers\Admin\*` (17 controllers) | Same — keeps admin logic isolated |
| **Feature Controllers** | `FollowController`, `CommentController`, `ReportController` | Reuse directly — social features are entity-agnostic |
| **Analytics in Middleware** | `TrackVisitors` middleware counts page views | Reuse — track movie page views similarly |

### 1.3 Routing Pattern (4 Groups)

```
Group 1: PUBLIC         — Accessible without login (homepage, detail, search, authors)
Group 2: AUTH           — Login, register, forgot password, OTP verification
Group 3: AUTH+VERIFIED  — Write reviews, like, comment, follow, save posts
Group 4: AUTH+ADMIN     — Full admin panel under /admin prefix
```

> **Movie Port:** Same 4-group pattern. Replace `sach/` prefix with `phim/` or `movies/`.

### 1.4 Key Model Relationships

```mermaid
erDiagram
    Book ||--o{ Post : "has many reviews"
    Post }|--|| User : "written by"
    Post ||--o{ Comment : "has comments"
    Post ||--o{ Like : "has likes"
    User ||--o{ Post : "writes"
    User }o--o{ User : "follows"
    User }o--o{ Post : "bookmarks (saved_posts)"
    User }o--o{ Badge : "earns"
    User }o--o{ Challenge : "joins"
    User }o--o{ AvatarFrame : "owns"
    Book }o--o{ Category : "belongs to"
    Book }o--o{ Author : "written by"
    Comment ||--o{ Comment : "replies (parent_id)"
    Comment ||--o{ CommentLike : "liked"
```

> **Movie Port:** Replace [Book](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/Book.php#10-98) with `Movie`, [Author](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/AuthorController.php#12-367) with `Actor/Director`, `Category` with `Genre`. The [Post](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/Post.php#9-77) model (reviews) maps directly.

