## 3. Feature Breakdown

### 3.1 Review System (Post Model + PostController)

| Feature | Implementation | Movie Adaptation |
|---------|---------------|-----------------|
| **Create Review** | Rich form: title, content, rating (1-5), thumbnail, book selection via AJAX search | Same — replace book search with movie search (TMDB API) |
| **Edit Review** | Separate edit view, only by author | Same |
| **Delete Workflow** | [requestDelete](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/PostController.php#283-327) → admin approval → [forceDelete](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/PostController.php#383-405) or [restorePost](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/PostController.php#359-382) | Same — prevents accidental content loss |
| **Status System** | `draft`, `pending`, `published`, `rejected`, `hidden`, `pending_delete` | Same — use for content moderation |
| **View Counting** | Session-based deduplication | Same |
| **Soft Deletes** | `SoftDeletes` trait on Post model | Same |

### 3.2 Rating System

- **Per-Review Rating:** Each [Post](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/Post.php#9-77) has a `rating` (float 1-5)
- **Book Average:** Calculated via `withAvg(['posts'], 'rating')` — not stored, computed on-the-fly
- **Display:** Star icons (full, half, empty) + numeric badge
- **Filter by Rating:** Search supports `having('posts_avg_rating', '>=', value)`

> **Movie Port:** Consider adding a 1-10 scale (Letterboxd style) or keeping 1-5 stars. Add separate ratings for story, visuals, acting, etc.

### 3.3 Comment System (Threaded)

- **Nested Comments:** `parent_id` nullable → supports replies
- **Comment Likes:** Separate `CommentLike` model
- **AJAX Loading:** Community comments loaded via AJAX with sort options
- **Notifications:** `CommentRepliedNotification`, `CommentLikedNotification`, `PostCommentedNotification`

### 3.4 Social Features

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Follow System** | Many-to-many self-referencing (`follows` pivot table), follower/following counts |
| **Bookmark/Save** | [savedPosts](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/User.php#44-51) pivot table, toggle via AJAX |
| **Like System** | Generic [Like](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/PostController.php#120-157) model for posts, separate `CommentLike` for comments |
| **Notifications** | 14 notification types: likes, comments, replies, follows, admin actions, reports |
| **User Profile** | Avatar, bio, badges, avatar frames, activity title, challenges, follower count |

### 3.5 Search & Filtering

| Filter Type | Behavior |
|-------------|----------|
| **Title Search** | `LIKE %keyword%` on title + author name |
| **By View Count** | `view_count >= value`, sorted desc |
| **By Avg Rating** | `HAVING posts_avg_rating >= value` |
| **By Total Reviews** | `HAVING posts_count >= value` |
| **Validation** | Rejects negative numbers, warns on special numbers (0, 13, 666) |

> **Movie Port:** Add filters for genre, year, runtime, language, director, actor.

### 3.6 Gamification System

| Feature | Model | Purpose |
|---------|-------|---------|
| **Challenges** | [Challenge](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/User.php#155-211), `UserChallenge` | Time-limited goals (e.g., "Review 5 books this month") |
| **Badges** | [Badge](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/User.php#103-115), `UserBadge` | Rewards for completing challenges, with expiry dates |
| **Avatar Frames** | [AvatarFrame](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/ProfileController.php#226-256), `UserAvatarFrame` | Cosmetic rewards, equip/unequip |
| **Activity Titles** | [ActivityTitle](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/User.php#141-154) | Auto-assigned based on published post + book count |
| **Ranking** | `RankingController` | Leaderboard by likes |

> **Movie Port:** "Watch Challenge" — watch and review N movies in a genre. "Film Buff" / "Cinephile" / "Critic" activity titles based on review count.

### 3.7 Admin Panel

17 admin controllers managing:
- **Dashboard** with analytics charts
- **Content Moderation:** Post approvals, rejections, delete requests
- **Entity CRUD:** Books, Authors, Categories, Articles, Banners, Quotes
- **Gamification:** Challenges, Badges, Avatar Frames, Activity Titles
- **Reporting:** Comment reports, post reports with resolution
- **User Management**
- **Theme Customization**
- **Activity Logs** with full audit trail
- **Subscribers**

### 3.8 Additional Features

| Feature | Notes |
|---------|-------|
| **AI Chatbot** | `ChatbotController` with history, clearable. Integrated as floating widget. |
| **Newsletter** | `SubscriberController` for email subscriptions |
| **Article/Blog** | Separate `Article` model for editorial content |
| **Book Suggestion** | Users can suggest books to add (`BookSuggestionController`) |
| **Seasonal Themes** | Auto-decorations for holidays (Christmas, Vietnamese New Year, Valentine, Halloween) |
| **Image Proxy** | CORS bypass for external author photos |

