## 4. User Flow

### 4.1 Discovery → Review Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Homepage] --> B{Browse}
    B --> C[Hero Carousel]
    B --> D[New Books Slider]
    B --> E[Search Page]
    B --> F[Category Sidebar]
    C & D & E & F --> G[Book Detail Page]
    G --> H{User Logged In?}
    H -- No --> I[See Reviews Only]
    H -- Yes --> J[Write Review]
    J --> K[Select Rating 1-5]
    K --> L[Write Title+Content]
    L --> M[Upload Thumbnail]
    M --> N[Submit → Status: pending]
    N --> O[Admin Approves → published]
    O --> P[Appears in Feeds]
```

### 4.2 Social Interaction Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Read Review on Book Detail] --> B[Like Review ❤️]
    A --> C[Comment on Review 💬]
    C --> D[Reply to Comment]
    A --> E[Save/Bookmark 🔖]
    A --> F[Report Content 🚩]
    A --> G[Visit Reviewer Profile]
    G --> H[Follow User]
    H --> I[Get Notifications for New Posts]
```

### 4.3 Gamification Flow

```
Join Challenge → Write Reviews in time window →
System calculates progress → 
If target met → Earn Badge + Avatar Frame →
Display on Profile
```

