## 5. Adaptation for Movie Review Website

### 5.1 Entity Mapping

| Góc Sách | Movie Portal | Changes |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| [Book](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/Book.php#10-98) | `Movie` | Add: runtime, trailer_url, backdrop_image, release_date, budget, revenue |
| [Author](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/AuthorController.php#12-367) | `Person` (actor/director/crew) | Add: role field, split into cast/crew |
| `Category` | `Genre` | Minimal changes |
| [Post](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Models/Post.php#9-77) (review) | [Review](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/gocsach-laravel/app/Http/Controllers/ProfileController.php#176-202) | Add: is_spoiler flag, compound rating (story/visuals/acting) |
| `Article` | `News/Editorial` | Same |
| `Bookshelf` | `Watchlist` | Same pattern |
| `Quote` | `MovieQuote` | Same |

### 5.2 New Features for Movies

| Feature | Description | Inspired By |
|---------|------------|-------------|
| **Trailer Embed** | YouTube/Vimeo embed on movie detail page | TMDB |
| **Backdrop Images** | Full-width hero images from movie stills | Letterboxd |
| **Cast & Crew** | Scrollable cards with actor photos and roles | TMDB |
| **"Where to Watch"** | Streaming platform availability | JustWatch |
