### 5.3 UI Adaptations

#### Hero Section
- **Books:** 3D tilted book cover with text beside it
- **Movies:** Full-width backdrop image with gradient overlay, trailer play button, movie poster overlay. Use cinematic widescreen aspect ratio (21:9)

#### Card Components
- **Book Card (2:3):** → **Movie Poster Card (2:3)** — keep same aspect ratio
- **Review Card (16:10):** → **Review Card with Movie Backdrop (16:9)** — use movie still as background
- Add a **Mini Rating Dial** (circular progress bar) instead of stars for movie scores

#### Detail Page
- **Books:** Cover + metadata + reviews listed below
- **Movies:** Backdrop hero → Poster + metadata row → Cast carousel → Trailer embed → Reviews section → Similar movies

#### Color & Theme
Replace the warm, literary palette with a dark, cinematic one:

```
Primary:    #0d1117 (GitHub dark background)
Surface:    #161b22 (elevated surfaces)
Accent:     #e94560 (Letterboxd-inspired red) or #f5c518 (IMDb gold)
Text:       #c9d1d9 (light gray)
Muted:      #8b949e
Success:    #3fb950
```

